&lt;p&gt;Following a review of our paediatric nursing structure we are excited to offer an opportunity for a highly motivated and experienced children&#39;s nurse to become our first epilepsy nurse specialist at Wexham Park hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have a paediatric clinical lead and link in with Oxford paediatric neurology team. We see a number of children with complex epilepsy who have been supported previously by a couple of our children&#39;s community team who had an interest in epilepsy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We will welcome you and provide an individual induction programme with access to continuing professional development opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be supported by a senior team including matrons and the Head of Nursing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ros Rushworth&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Head of nursing&lt;/p&gt;
